      "title" : "Github: Commit, Push, Merge",
      "updatedAt" : "2026-07-02T22:15:10Z",
      "value" : "Commit all changes and push them to the remote. If working on a branch other than main, merge the branch into main after validation, push main, then delete the merged branch locally and remotely.",
